"""crunchyroll-api - single-file bundle.

Unofficial Crunchyroll API (library) bundled into one module so it can be copied
directly into another project. Generated by build_single_file.py - do not edit by
hand; edit the package under src/crunchyroll_api/ and rebuild.

Only runtime dependency: requests.

Quick start:
    from crunchyroll_api import CrunchyrollClient, CrunchyrollFinder

    client = CrunchyrollClient(email="a@b.de", password="secret", locale="de-DE")
    client.login()
    series = client.search_series("Frieren")
"""

